WordCloud of Directors¶

In [244]:
from wordcloud import WordCloud
In [245]:
directors = ' '.join(df['Director'].dropna().astype(str))

wordcloud = WordCloud(width=800, height=400, background_color='white').generate(directors)


plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
plt.imshow(wordcloud, interpolation='bilinear')
plt.axis('off')  
plt.title('Word Cloud of Directors')
plt.show()

Average Ratings by Directors¶

In [246]:
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
In [261]:
plt.figure(figsize=(20, 16))
director_ratings = df.groupby('Director')['Rating'].mean()
director_ratings.plot(kind='bar', color='skyblue')

plt.title('Average Ratings by Directors')
plt.xlabel('Director')
plt.ylabel('Average Rating')


plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MultipleLocator(base=10))  

plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')  
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

df['Hero'] = df['Hero'].apply(lambda x: x.split(',')[0] if pd.notnull(x) else None)

hero_counts = df['Hero'].value_counts()
heroine_counts = df['Heroine'].value_counts()

df_cleaned = df.dropna(subset=['Runtime'])

df_cleaned['Runtime'] = pd.to_numeric(df_cleaned['Runtime'], errors='coerce')


mean_runtime = df_cleaned['Runtime'].mean()
median_runtime = df_cleaned['Runtime'].median()
mode_runtime = df_cleaned['Runtime'].mode()[0]  

print(f"Mean Runtime: {mean_runtime:.2f} minutes")
print(f"Median Runtime: {median_runtime:.2f} minutes")
print(f"Mode Runtime: {mode_runtime:.2f} minutes")
